OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry with plenty of sunshine.
OL,6,FHowever, cloudier skies across eastern
OL,7,FScotland and northeast England. The
OL,8,Fodd shower may also develop across
OL,9,FCornwall. Feeling pleasant in the
OL,10,Fsheltered west but chilly in the east.
OL,11,FStrong and gusty winds in the
OL,12,Fsouthwest.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FDry with clear spells.
OL,15,FCloudiest skies across eastern
OL,16,FScotland and northeast England. A
OL,17,Fpatchy frost possible in the
OL,18,Fcountryside. Remaining breezy across
OL,19,Fsouthwest England.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
