OL,5,CThursday:FMorning low cloud lifting to
OL,6,Fleave a fine day, with plenty of
OL,7,Fsunshine. Still breezy in the
OL,8,Fsouthwest. Warm for most, but
OL,9,Fremaining chilly along eastern coasts.
